msgctxt "9816_Rio"
msgid "I don't think I'm really getting it."
msgstr "No creo entenderlo."

msgctxt "9828_Akiyama"
msgid "For example, someone might carry himself in a way that makes him seem dangerous and reckless."
msgstr "Por ejemplo, alguien puede comportarse de un modo que le haga parecer peligroso e imprudente."

msgctxt "9840_Akiyama"
msgid "He could be the nicest guy in the world, but all people are gonna see is this dangerous man."
msgstr "Podría ser el tipo más amable del mundo, pero lo único que la gente va a ver es a ese hombre peligroso."

msgctxt "9852_Rio"
msgid "I guess so..."
msgstr "Supongo..."

msgctxt "9864_Akiyama"
msgid "On the other hand, say someone carries himself in a mellow way that just makes him seem very nonthreatening."
msgstr "Por otro lado, supongamos que alguien se comporta de una manera tranquila que simplemente lo hace parecer muy inofensivo."

msgctxt "9876_Akiyama"
msgid "No one's going to be on their guard when someone like that shows up."
msgstr "Nadie estará en guardia cuando aparezca una persona así."

msgctxt "9888_Rio"
msgid "Oh! I think I see where you're going with this!"
msgstr "¡Oh! ¡Creo que sé a dónde quieres llegar con esto!"

